{"tid":1640926,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抗爭運動進入樽頸的原因及解決方法","createTime":"2019-10-09T07:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T10:01:14.000Z","uid":61886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4c92c9cdbb4086ec5eff6f00338e1cad1b2f40a9","tid":1640926,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:34:09.000Z","msg":"今個星期行動post極少<br />\n星期六日亦無大型活動<br />\n<br />\n以下先貼行程表文宣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yCgAhch.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyCgAhch.jpg&h=fe1c04fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原因如下：<br />\n1. 舉辦唔到大型遊行，每次損兵折將<br />\n解決方法：以不同主題舉辦集會，例如之前新屋嶺、公務員、中學生集會等，保持抗爭溫度。<br />\n<br />\n2. 18區開花被警犬壓制同滲透<br />\n解決方法：以商場唱歌為集合點，先聚集人氣，再決定行動。<br />\n<br />\n3. 黨鐵協助宵禁<br />\n解決方法：以地區形式組織不同地區活動，包括放映會、座談會、修復連儂牆等。<br />\n<br />\n4. 活動欠缺創意<br />\n解決方法：要靠各位手足提供創意活動。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論"},{"pid":"951c7f35a45800cd4d4890add33ddda4fc4c6565","tid":1640926,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:13:59.000Z","msg":"解決方法在此<br />\n<br />\n大家係時係建立社區抗爭組織，唔係為做政治show，而係為咗整合依場運動嘅資源，實現民主自治！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1617406\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1617406</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b6293cbdffacc489f30fe5d6ac56225f17508197","tid":1640926,"uid":21920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:15:05.000Z","msg":"各區開花都要有原因先推到"},{"pid":"a7926a59c312394cc3e81a5077528fc8c8c536a0","tid":1640926,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:01:14.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}